          <td valign="top">

<span class="txth1">halfmove : Move the cursor half way up or down the screen</span> 

<br>
<br>

<!-- karma table -->
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" border="1" bordercolor="#000066">
<tr>
  <td class="lightbg"><b>&nbsp;script karma&nbsp;</b></td>
  <td>
    Rating <b>0/0</b>,
    Downloaded by 164  </td>
  <td class="lightbg">
  <b>&nbsp;Comments, bugs, improvements&nbsp;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
    <a href="http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Script:1981">Vim wiki</a>
  </td>  
</tr>
</table>
<p>

<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
<tr><td class="prompt">created by</td></tr>
<tr><td><a href="/account/profile.php?user_id=9971">Andy Spencer</a></td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td class="prompt">script type</td></tr>
<tr><td>utility</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td class="prompt">description</td></tr>
<tr><td>Vim script to move the cursor half way down/up the screen. This can be<br>thought of as a binary search for a line that is visible in the window by<br>either moving up or down.<br><br>Created:	2007 Aug 05<br>Last Change:	2007 Aug 05<br>Author:	Andy Spencer &lt;andy753421 at gmail dot com&gt;<br>Thanks To:	#vim@irc.freenode.net<br><br>Usage:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Press &lt;C-K&gt; to jump half way to the top of the screen<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Press &lt;C-J&gt; to jump half way to the bottom of the screen<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Pressing &lt;C-[KJ]&gt; several times in a row will jump halfway to the<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;top/bottom or half way to a previous jump location.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Example: To jump 3/8 of the way to the bottom of the screen press<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;C-J&gt;&lt;C-K&gt;&lt;C-J&gt;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Customization:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;map &lt;silent&gt; &lt;YOUR-DOWN-KEY&gt; :call HM_Move(&quot;down&quot;)&lt;CR&gt;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;map &lt;silent&gt; &lt;YOUR-UP-KEY&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp; :call HM_Move(&quot;up&quot;)&lt;CR&gt;<br><br>Problems:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;C-J&gt; and &lt;C-K&gt; will not be mapped over existing mappings. If other<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;scripts map &lt;C-J&gt; or &lt;C-K&gt; then you will need to manually override those.</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr><td class="prompt">install details</td></tr>
<tr><td>Add this file to $RUNTIME/plugins</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

